reviews.text: Gordon hill station, well it's an average station it has some weak spots like the way you walk to the station building to the platform the bridge looks like it needs an update. It's got some nice waiting rooms, also it has a vending machine only on the platform heading to central London.

Workmen have been doing road works on this road during the day and it’s causing chaos. They stupidly start around 09.00 and are there till around 16.00, blocking the whole road one way. Why don’t they do it in the evening?. They sit around in their vans resting, drinking tea and basically taking up space on the road. This is Enfield council for you.
